      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONLY EASY (2) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and five minors from 17 tries. Hit the frame latest (20.33) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Rates on top and should go close. ATHLETE TICK (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (21.78) from Box 5 at Q Lakeside. Goes very well from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from 10 starts. Expected to feature again. JET SPRINGER (8) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Shifty Breeze (20.00) in a Mix 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to be in the finish again. MISS RIGHTEOUS (3) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
